text: Ðis synd ða landgemæro ðæra þreora hida æt Bysceopes stoce.
Ærest on ðæs heges hyrnan be Westan stoce.
Of ðam on ða ealdan dic on haran mære norðwardne.
Of haran mære innan filidleage norðwarde.
Of filidleage norðward in ðone holan broc.
Of ðæm holan broce innan sweoperlan stream.
Of sweoperlan streame on dinningcgrafes wyrttruman.
Of dynningcgrafes wyrttruman eall swa se dic sceot on esnig mædwæ wearde.
Of esnig mædwan eal swa ðæt ealde riðig sceot up on ðone ealdan hearpað.
Of ðæm ealdan hearpaðe up on ða ealdan dic wið stoces weard.
Of ðære ealdan dic eal swa se hege sceot be stoce westan eft on ðæs heges hyrnan.
Geanbec into Gleweceaster æt Bisceopes stoce.
